        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix: skip default idle heartbeat without HEARTBEAT.md",
        "body": "Summary\n- Skip default, unconfigured idle heartbeat runs when the agent workspace has no HEARTBEAT.md, no due commitments, and no event wake payload.\n- Preserve existing behavior for explicit heartbeat configuration and wake/cron/exec-triggered runs.\n- Add a regression test proving the default missing-file idle path does not call the LLM or send outbound messages.\n- Update heartbeat and troubleshooting docs for the new `missing-heartbeat-file` skip reason.\n\nFixes #85210\n\nVerification\n- `OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/heartbeat-runner.returns-default-unset.test.ts`\n- `corepack pnpm format:check docs/gateway/heartbeat.md docs/gateway/troubleshooting.md docs/help/faq-first-run.md docs/help/troubleshooting.md`\n- `git diff --check`\n- `git diff --cached --check`\n\n## Real behavior proof\n\nBehavior addressed: default 30m heartbeat should not burn model tokens while idle when the user has not opted into heartbeat instructions and HEARTBEAT.md is absent.\n\nReal environment tested: Windows checkout, current `origin/main` merged into this branch, repo dependencies installed with Corepack pnpm 11.2.2.\n\nExact steps or command run after this patch: `OPENCLAW_VITEST_MAX_WORKERS=1 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/heartbeat-runner.returns-default-unset.test.ts`\n\nEvidence after fix: terminal output from the refreshed Windows checkout running `node scripts/run-vitest.mjs src/infra/heartbeat-runner.returns-default-unset.test.ts`:\n\n```text\nRUN  v4.1.7 C:/Users/atusa/OneDrive/Desktop/Openclaw\n\nTest Files  1 passed (1)\n     Tests  40 passed (40)\n  Start at  07:32:11\n  Duration  11.51s (transform 5.41s, setup 473ms, import 7.04s, tests 3.82s, environment 0ms)\n```\n\nObserved result after fix: the missing HEARTBEAT.md default-idle scenario returns `skipped/missing-heartbeat-file`; the run verifies zero `getReplyFromConfig` LLM calls and zero outbound sends for that path.\n\nWhat was not tested: live gateway idle soak against z.ai/glm-5.1 token usage.\n",
